{"tid":523193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位覺得自己係選民既港豬入一入黎","createTime":"2018-01-08T09:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T16:34:40.000Z","uid":1477,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8a128ae80ee888cf89289375ecdb9f1695513c","tid":523193,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:53:26.000Z","msg":"一年前我返過選舉事務處，從中得知幾件事，希望提返大家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 有好多人因為無回覆住址證明書，於是比人cancel 左選民資格<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n咁你要做既就係去Check下到底你係咪選民<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/regulations.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2Fregulations.jsp&d=AQXv8v5zrInziDiuWMdLC2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5fe834c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/regulations.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n正常就會係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/174045_2fe543744055b5bc3f0b4283f02c4f83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F174045_2fe543744055b5bc3f0b4283f02c4f83.png&h=17acd8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到你有區議會同立法會既選民資格<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 留意返你既「功能組別」係有無野，假設你唔係專業界別既選民，但最起碼你應該係區議會（第二）功能界別<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n區議會（第二）功能界別姐係所謂既超級區議會，就算你唔係專業界別，你都可以係超級區議會既選民<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，區議會（第二）功能界別不包括因所屬界別候選人自動當選而失去投票機會的選民，而若本身是其他功能界別的選民若登記了此界別，將會失去其原功能界別的選民資格。<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，姐係你選擇投超級區議會，你就無得投返自己個界別<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3. 如果你發覺自己無功能界別資格，又唔係超級區議會既選民，咁得一個可能性</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n個可能性就係你個on9仔，死港豬，係填果張選民登格剔左紅框既果一格<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/174842_402addca6baf71bbd4575f2ef8d9ce4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F174842_402addca6baf71bbd4575f2ef8d9ce4e.png&h=c55ba454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可能會話，你肯定無剔到，係港共屈鳩你<br />\n<br />\n但唔係囉，每一份選民登記既表格，都會scan入電腦留返份soft copy<br />\n<br />\n有極多人都堅稱自己剔左做區議會（第二）功能界別既選民，但事實係，你條撚樣剔左唔做<br />\n<br />\n麻煩填form果陣真係睇清楚呀屌你<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住呢格唔撚好剔左佢<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4. 舊年好多後生既人打上黎問點解投唔到票<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n原因好簡單，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你根本無登記過</span>"},{"pid":"9ceeabf41b984c37d857c2f25a25875cae8b7e84","tid":523193,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:18:02.000Z","msg":"無人理就算"},{"pid":"31ce2a6b25c64f65ab5f87c96de354f168056daa","tid":523193,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09303665948576ee9f279a923b09d7248bd34d4","tid":523193,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31ce2a6b25c64f65ab5f87c96de354f168056daa","tid":523193,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7be379f3b4c8e03287d5eee9235a2f876cd251e","tid":523193,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2376b4c27e76eb56325e5b36a5dfe7e595178e1d","tid":523193,"uid":60408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:56:35.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cbb18d8e9b516efcd5e518e1240b4959ea1248","tid":523193,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"一推再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2